29
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:18,050
"Although I Love You, And You?"

30
00:02:19,170 --> 00:02:19,780
Alright.

31
00:02:20,510 --> 00:02:21,700
It's no good.

32
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:23,990
Oh.

