Sorry for making you wait.

35
00:02:31,570 --> 00:02:33,620
Sorry. Have you been waiting for long?

36
00:02:39,130 --> 00:02:40,050
Sakae-kun.

37
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:41,260
Ah, hello.

38
00:02:43,130 --> 00:02:45,190
So this is how he dresses casually.

39
00:02:45,570 --> 00:02:47,180
Sorry for dragging you along.

40
00:02:47,180 --> 00:02:48,500
No worries.

41
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:50,090
Alright, shall we go?

42
00:02:50,420 --> 00:02:52,580
- Yes. This way.
- Yeah.

43
