50
00:03:15,210 --> 00:03:16,290
Nothing's coming to mind,

51
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:17,890
so that's the problem.

52
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,090
Huh?

53
00:03:19,570 --> 00:03:22,450
Nothing, I'll try to draw something.

54
00:03:23,460 --> 00:03:24,120
Yeah.

55
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:33,850
That is...

56
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:35,400
Melonpan.

57
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:37,910
I see.

58
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:41,380
It's a melon yet not a melon,

59
00:03:41,830 --> 00:03:43,025
within you,

60
00:03:43,073 --> 00:03:45,233
- representing the truth and lies...
- It's not...

61
00:03:45,260 --> 00:03:46,250
That kind of thing.

62
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:48,860
I'm embarrassed, please stop.

63
00:03:49,020 --> 00:03:50,310
It's not embarrassing.

64
00:03:50,510 --> 00:03:51,790
I think it is wonderful,

65
00:03:51,790 --> 00:03:52,770
your drawing.

66
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,530
I think art

67
00:04:00,810 --> 00:04:02,413
isn't something lofty,

68
00:04:02,438 --> 00:04:04,953
it's something very close to us.

69
00:04:05,770 --> 00:04:09,270
- Oh, I see what you mean.
- Yeah.

70
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:12,820
- Sorry, excuse me for a moment.
- Hmm?

71
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:20,960
I see,

72
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,490
even this flower is considered art.

73
00:04:25,250 --> 00:04:27,090
No matter the environment,

74
00:04:27,620 --> 00:04:28,740
